title: Path planning vital for Brisbane's active lifestyle
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › Path planning vital for Brisbane's ac... Path planning vital for Brisbane's active lifestyle 2 hrs ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
THE new riverwalk from the CBD to New Farm is a sign of what must come as we continue our love affair with inner-city living and the walking and cycling that goes with it. Aside from building a secure pathway unlikely to be washed away, the designers have also had the good sense to clearly partition the cycling and walking areas of the riverwalk.   Sydney Morning Herald.
